pullrequest.title: X3 Sensor Config 2 Submission by SSCI

content.raw:
Due to time constraints, this configuration will not be incorporated before the code freeze, but new IMU models will be considered for future events.

Would you like to keep this PR open for consideration after Urban Circuit?

pullrequest.title: X3 Sensor Config 2 Submission by SSCI

content.raw:
This model is not expected to be incorporated for the Cave Circuit to encourage teams to use alternate and multi-modal sensing approaches to overcome the challenges presented by noisy IMU data.  
Other UAV models are available with upward/downward range data.
